sys_element_mapping.value:
action➛Previous Mission Owner Name transferred ownership of a JWCC requirements package to you

 

action➛Previous Mission Owner Name made you the owner of “action➛...➛Title” within the DISA Acquisition Package Preparation System (DAPPS). As the owner, you can now:

  • Submit this package to a Contracting Office for processing
  • Manage contributor access
  • Archive or delete this package

Access package from your dashboard: https://services.disa.mil/atat

 

This was sent from an unmonitored email address. Please do not reply to this email. If you have questions about JWCC or DAPPS, please contact our Customer Support Team at https://community.hacc.mil/s/contact?&RoleType=Customer
